description:
The Box - Series 1, Episode 2




Three enthusiastic home cooks are pitted against each other as they try to make a delicious dish using the day's ingredient boxes. The first test is to create something from a box put together by Lord Sugar's right-hand woman, the formidable Margaret Mountford. In the second challenge, James Martin selects the ingredients to go into three new boxes. Based on the dishes from this second test, James Martin decides who triumphs and wins Cook of the Day!




Original Air Date: 26-May-2015
